comment: https://www.yeastgenome.org/strain/S000203501. YPS163 was isolated in 1999 from the soil beneath an oak tree (Quercus rubra) in a Pennsylvania woodland. YPS163 is freeze tolerant, a phenotype associated with its increased expression of aquaporin AQY2.
